
config SPRD_CAMERA_CSI_RECEIVER_R2P0
    bool "Spreadtrum Camera Sprd CSI2 RECEIVER R2P0"
    depends on SPRD_CAMERA
    help
        This is a CSI conecting synopsys DPHY driver for Spreadtrum SOCs.

